title: Did not get Season Rewards. Support Ticket gave me copy-paster answer.
body:
Literally just copied the "End of Season"-FAQ.

Can I get some real help, please?

http://i.imgur.com/mCsH2pP.jpg

Where have my rewards gone? No chat restriction or any of that nonsense.

replies.body: I do see you have a few tickets on this, and replying to the original ticket should ping your specialist to get back to you.  Things have been happening pretty quickly, as well as running waves to get rewards out.  Hang tight!
